{
    "abstract": "In this demo, we present ConsciousControlFlow(CCF), a prototype system to demonstrate conscious Artificial Intelligence (AI). The system is based on the computational model for consciousness and the hierarchy of needs. CCF supports typical scenarios to show the behaviors and the mental activities of conscious AI. We demonstrate that CCF provides a useful tool for effective machine consciousness demonstration and human behavior study assistance.",
